  sodium: 1450 mg
author: Michelle Doll Olson
servings: 2
time required: 25 minutes
cuisine: North America
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/old-school-bbq-pork-sloppy-joes-5f98816c10a5df1eb416ebd1
course: main course
